# Admin UI

- Preserve diagnostics; failed import ≠ published destination (separate badges/states).
- Actions explicit (POST); no silent mutation on GET/page load.
- Loading, error, permission-denied, empty states required.
- Use `adminGet`/`adminPost`; handle 401/403 via session flow.
- No broad visual redesign unless requested; Russian admin copy.

## Key areas

Imports (`AdminImportJobsPage`), discovery, debug reports (`AdminDebugReportsPage`), destinations, places moderation.
